clearly,

00:25:17.866 --> 00:25:22.353
because He knew that somebody has to come,

00:25:22.554 --> 00:25:27.222
and He said the Holy Ghost will come,

00:25:27.423 --> 00:25:30.702
and She’ll have three things as you know:

00:25:30.903 --> 00:25:37.425
that She’ll be a Comforter, She’ll be
a Counselor, and She’ll be a Redeemer.

00:25:37.626 --> 00:25:44.500
He didn’t use She or He, but in Hebrew
language it says “It”.

00:25:45.132 --> 00:25:50.287
So people have misused Bible to such
an extent that in England

00:25:50.488 --> 00:25:55.870
a king wanted to divorce his wife so he
authorized the Bible.

00:25:56.071 --> 00:26:02.367
How can such an adharmic fellow authorize
such a holy book like Bible?

00:26:02.603 --> 00:26:08.314
Because the power: with the power he want
to control,

00:26:08.514 --> 00:26:13.797
want to control all that is reality.

00:26:13.998 --> 00:26:16.587
This is a blind power.

00:26:16.788 --> 00:26:22.443
But if you have a real power, then you know
what to respect, what not to respect.

00:26:22.644 --> 00:26:24.783
Which way to go, which way not to go.

00:26:24.984 --> 00:26:32.838
Because you have a sight, you know a very
bright understanding of the whole thing.

00:26:33.039 --> 00:26:40.349
Which road you have to follow, where you
have to go, and which is the right thing.

00:26:40.550 --> 00:26:46.063
Thank God through this Kali Yuga, because
of all kinds of horrible things,

00:26:46.264 --> 00:26:51.631
as also among Hindus lots of funny, funny
rituals they have,

00:26:51.832 --> 00:26:58.620
that people have seen through that this is
not the end of it.

00:26:58.821 --> 00:27:02.363
You have to seek, you have to seek.

00:27:02.580 --> 00:27:08.396
But the only thing which is very important
is that all of them have said

00:27:08.597 --> 00:27:12.922
that you have to seek, you have to find out
your Self.

00:27:13.123 --> 00:27:18.040
Which is very clearly written in some
of the Indian scriptures.

00:27:18.241 --> 00:27:21.138
Some of them, I would say not all of them.

00:27:21.339 --> 00:27:24.539
Some of them it is written that you must
seek your Self,

00:27:24.740 --> 00:27:29.535
specially the saints who came on this earth
in India,

00:27:29.736 --> 00:27:35.929
they have tried to say all the time that
you must seek,

00:27:36.130 --> 00:27:39.597
you must find out the truth. Because they
knew the truth

00:27:39.798 --> 00:27:42.796
and they wanted others to find the truth.

00:27:42.997 --> 00:27:46.877
So in every religion there have been
enlightened people.

00:27:47.078 --> 00:27:53.843
Among Buddhists also there has been
a Viditama, Lao-Tse, and many others,

00:27:54.044 --> 00:27:59.483
who have talked about seeking, seeking
the truth.

00:27:59.685 --> 00:28:03.849
Christ has said it very clearly, very, very
clearly,

00:28:04.050 --> 00:28:11.035
and at His birthday I feel very happy that
so many of you

00:28:11.236 --> 00:28:15.011
have already found out the truth and that
you know

00:28:15.212 --> 00:28:19.729
the path of love and compassion and
humility.

00:28:19.930 --> 00:28:24.774
As it is we know where Christ resides
within us,

00:28:24.975 --> 00:28:29.221
and how to respect Christ, and how
to worship it.

00:28:29.422 --> 00:28:32.991
With this Agnya chakra you can make out
a person

00:28:33.192 --> 00:28:41.838
whether he is a seeker or he is
a dominating arrogant Christian.

00:28:42.912 --> 00:28:46.562
You cannot do that, if you are a Christian
you cannot be that.

00:28:46.763 --> 00:28:49.414
If you are that, then you are not
a Christian.

00:28:49.615 --> 00:28:52.267
Look at Christ, how humble He was.

00:28:52.468 --> 00:28:57.226
He could have finished them off - He had
such powers - all of them;

00:28:57.427 --> 00:29:05.126
but He got Himself crucified. The reason
was Agnya chakra was to be broken.

00:29:05.327 --> 00:29:08.888
Was to be crossed. And so He accepted.

00:29:09.089 --> 00:29:12.188
As I told you He had all the powers
of Shri Ganesha,

00:29:12.389 --> 00:29:19.231
which are the most destructive powers.

00:29:19.432 --> 00:29:24.038
All these powers come from Mother Earth,

00:29:24.239 --> 00:29:28.582
and the Mother Earth can shake the whole
world.

00:29:28.783 --> 00:29:33.095
But He was the One who came as Mahavishnu,

00:29:33.283 --> 00:29:38.320
as described in the Devi Mahatmya. What
a person He was,

00:29:38.521 --> 00:29:43.122
and what He did, all His work is
beautifully described in Mahavishnu.

00:29:43.974 --> 00:29:50.856
Now, when they do not know, want to connect the Devi Mahatmya with Christ’s work,

00:29:51.294 --> 00:29:54.770
it’s alright, they are lost.

00:29:54.833 --> 00:29:59.544
There’s such a disintegration, and there’s no collectivity, nothing.

00:29:59.786 --> 00:30:05.994
And they call themselves as the disciples of Christ: you cannot.

00:30:06.581 --> 00:30:09.089
You must have love, compassion.

00:30:09.230 --> 00:30:14.058
And not for a purpose. They have missionaries who go and

00:30:14.214 --> 00:30:20.665
talk of compassion, love, and what they achieve is nothing but conversion, because

00:30:20.697 --> 00:30:24.533
it is democracy and they want to have more heads.

00:30:24.613 --> 00:30:29.953
It’s so despising, the whole attitude towards Christ,

00:30:30.094 --> 00:30:35.273
is so criminal to have such an attitude towards Christ,

00:30:35.352 --> 00:30:39.522
who was the One who came to give salvation to the whole world,

00:30:40.053 --> 00:30:45.670
to unite the whole world, and to make so many different, different

00:30:45.694 --> 00:30:49.420
efforts to spoil His name.

00:30:49.850 --> 00:30:57.090
Now I would tell you this, that if Christ
is born and He came on this earth,

00:30:57.291 --> 00:30:59.918
it’s a very, very great occasion.

00:31:00.119 --> 00:31:03.237
He gave His life for us, He did everything.

00:31:03.438 --> 00:31:08.018
And how are we following Him is
by forgiving.

00:31:08.219 --> 00:31:13.961
You have to forgive others, you forgive
yourself and you forgive others.

00:31:14.162 --> 00:31:18.259
Is very important if you want to open this
Agnya chakra,

00:31:18.460 --> 00:31:22.971
where resides our Lord Jesus Christ.

00:31:23.172 --> 00:31:26.483
If you cannot forgive others

00:31:26.684 --> 00:31:31.660
and you cannot forgive yourself, then this
Agnya won’t open.

00:31:31.861 --> 00:31:36.515
And the best part of it, all the Christian
nations I have seen,

00:31:36.724 --> 00:31:42.579
where there are so-called Christians, they
all have a very bad Agnya.

00:31:42.780 --> 00:31:48.418
If they are really following Christ, why
should there be a catch on the Agnya chakra?

00:31:48.619 --> 00:31:55.937
And they are extremely dominating, arrogant
people.

00:31:56.296 --> 00:32:02.125
They cannot be the disciples of Christ.
He was so humble,

00:32:02.326 --> 00:32:10.062
He was so much one with God Almighty, that
He accepted His crucifixion.

00:32:10.263 --> 00:32:15.260
His birth itself is a very great miracle,

00:32:15.461 --> 00:32:18.497
and His work is even greater.

00:32:18.698 --> 00:32:24.910
We have to win over all the Christians and
tell them what is real Christianity,

00:32:25.111 --> 00:32:28.751
what is reality, and what they should
take to,

00:32:28.952 --> 00:32:34.103
and how they should justify their following
of Christ.

00:32:34.304 --> 00:32:41.096
It is very big organizational thing, and
it’s a big, I mean, political thing,

00:32:41.297 --> 00:32:47.354
I mean, all kinds of things are going on.
And all the bad things they have

00:32:47.555 --> 00:32:51.878
from, say Hindu religion, they carry on.

00:32:52.101 --> 00:32:55.851
So what is the use of conversion also?

00:32:56.052 --> 00:33:03.366
So from His life we have to learn that
He took a birth

00:33:03.653 --> 00:33:10.906
in such a situation that nobody would have
dared to be born like that.

00:33:11.107 --> 00:33:16.730
So much of darkness and ignorance, so much
of cruelty,

00:33:16.931 --> 00:33:21.902
that He took His birth at that time is
extremely remarkable.

00:33:22.103 --> 00:33:25.730
Such a brave, courageous personality.

00:33:25.954 --> 00:33:29.434
Nowadays they make Christ look like
a TB patient, I mean,

00:33:29.635 --> 00:33:36.439
just to beg, you know. Because they are
beggars. All the time they are begging.

00:33:36.640 --> 00:33:43.153
And I was in Bombay this time, some little,
little girls and boys were singing songs

00:33:43.354 --> 00:33:47.247
and they came up, and they said, “Give us
some money.”

00:33:47.448 --> 00:33:50.004
I said, “What are you doing?”
“We are singing carols.”

00:33:50.205 --> 00:33:53.181
“So you sing! Why do you need money for?”

00:33:53.382 --> 00:33:58.336
“You know, we need money, we have no food
to eat.” Imagine.

00:33:58.537 --> 00:34:03.915
Then why sing songs of Christ?

00:34:04.806 --> 00:34:11.664
All kinds of begging is done. Christ, did
He beg for anything?

00:34:11.865 --> 00:34:15.553
Did He want to create beggars on this
earth?

00:34:15.754 --> 00:34:20.980
He died, lived with self-respect.

00:34:21.181 --> 00:34:26.064
All His qualities are never studied and
people take

00:34:26.265 --> 00:34:35.362
to something which is very mundane,
sometimes absolutely degrading, degrading.

00:34:35.563 --> 00:34:41.230
He came to give us a very dharmic,

00:34:41.439 --> 00:34:46.449
very… I shouldn’t say religious because
that's different meaning,

00:34:46.650 --> 00:34:52.585
but I would say a very pious and beautiful
life.

00:34:52.786 --> 00:34:56.787
He is the model, He is the model we have
to follow.

00:34:57.364 --> 00:35:02.254
Not that to become beggars and go round and ask for alms.

00:35:02.755 --> 00:35:08.106
Even in the schools which are Christian schools they teach this to children, that

00:35:08.310 --> 00:35:11.059
you go and ask for money, ask for money;

00:35:11.084 --> 00:35:13.473
all over the world they are asking for money.

00:35:13.560 --> 00:35:16.473
And what do they do with their money God only knows.

00:35:16.536 --> 00:35:22.254
Money can never be so important, never so important

00:35:22.518 --> 00:35:30.040
– it is just that we use it, but it cannot dominate us.

00:35:32.267 --> 00:35:36.900
He came in a very, very humble way, in a manger He was born,

00:35:37.088 --> 00:35:39.554
to show that money is not important.

