Though in the Sanskrit literature it is written that a God, or God Almighty when He incarnates,

00:35:51.611 --> 00:35:59.611
He has aishwarya, means He has wealth,
He must have wealth.

00:36:00.709 --> 00:36:04.201
It is meaning the spiritual wealth.

00:36:04.240 --> 00:36:07.740
He must be born with the spiritual wealth.

00:36:07.958 --> 00:36:13.498
If he has spiritual wealth, then He is the real incarnation.

00:36:14.115 --> 00:36:18.394
If you don’t have the spiritual wealth of love and compassion,

00:36:18.825 --> 00:36:24.043
and detachment, you cannot be called as an incarnation.

00:36:24.200 --> 00:36:31.043
It’s a myth. So we have to test it on people who are saying they are incarnations,

00:36:31.067 --> 00:36:35.238
they are gods, they are divine, that they will take you to divine life.

00:36:35.262 --> 00:36:37.777
See their own lives, how they live.

00:36:38.989 --> 00:36:41.129
See their own temperament.

00:36:42.641 --> 00:36:45.383
You can see how Christ knew about:

00:36:45.448 --> 00:36:49.875
